&lt;p&gt;You will leverage policy developments, tentpole campaigns, budget cycles, and champion networks to accelerate adoption — then ensure a smooth handoff to the Implementation &amp;amp; Success team for rollout. Success in this role means growing the number of districts and schools actively implementing Code.org&#39;s curriculum within your territory.&lt;/p&gt;
