&lt;li&gt;Navigate district decision-making processes, including curriculum reviews and procurement cycles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and cultivate internal district champions such as principals, teacher leaders, and technology leaders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate peer connections between prospective districts and successful adopters&lt;/li&gt;
