&lt;p&gt;At CodeAI, we&#39;re dedicated to broadening access to computer science and AI education in every classroom. To scale our impact, we&#39;re seeking a Senior Product Manager to lead the cross-functional development and end-to-end delivery of products and features that expand access to AI and computer science learning for K-12 students and teachers. In this role, you&#39;ll own outcomes for a domain within the CodeAI product focused on secondary student learning—developing deep customer and domain expertise, defining strategy and roadmaps, and partnering closely with engineering, design, curriculum, and data to ship features that achieve measurable goals for teachers, students, and the organization. You&#39;ll operate with significant independence in a remote and asynchronous environment, communicating crisply to align stakeholders and drive clarity through ambiguity. Grounded in the realities of public school classrooms, you&#39;ll keep teachers and students at the center of every product decision.&lt;/p&gt;
